title: Dinosaurs
description: From Diploducus to Compsognathus, these hungry dinosaurs are waiting for you! Sound effects are optional, but "Crunch" is always a good one.This colorful and sturdy board book with a circle cut out for a child's (or adult's) face is just about the best, most original way to introduce boks - and dinosaurs - since the Jurassic period!
author: Bénédicte Guettier
